info.description:
Atrack is designed to be a fast and efficient implementation of an 'universal
subset' of the BitTorrent tracker protocol (aka 'ntrack') for Google's App Engine.

For performance and privacy reasons it stores no data of any kind and relies

info.name: atrack
info.summary: A minimalist high performance tracker for App Engine.
info.html_description:
Atrack is designed to be a fast and efficient implementation of an ‘universal subset’ of the BitTorrent tracker protocol (aka ‘ntrack’) for Google’s App Engine.

For performance and privacy reasons it stores no data of any kind and relies solely on memcache.
